      .notes Notes.
        %ol
          %li Items can be dragged to reorder, or dragged from/to bin.
          %li If items can be dragged in/out of bin, is there any reason keeping the delete/restore buttons?
          %li Drag left-side tree to reorder.
          %li Drag from left-side into editor's parent/child sections.
          %li Reorder children via right-side children view.


